    "rationale": "All thirteen credibility factors have been evaluated under the Minimal profile. Seven factors were formally assessed; all achieved levels fall below required levels for MRL 5, and six factors remain as documented epistemic gaps. The package is accepted as a complete credibility evidence record under the Minimal profile, with the understanding that the overall V&V 40 submission decision remains Not Accepted pending resolution of factor gaps identified herein.",
